{"tid":618068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★雙失三年打機度日 90後自縊亡　","createTime":"2018-04-05T13:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T16:47:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14dcf00d8f75f1beb06e3d4fd5a3cd693d8e943c","tid":618068,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"今日（5日）早上6時許，有行山人士報案指，元朗大棠郊野公園楓香林一個涼亭，發現一名年約20歲的青年，用爬山繩吊頸自殺。警員接報到場，消防員立即將男事主解下，並為他進行急救，惜已返魂乏術。現場消息指，男事主年約20餘歲，與家人同住元朗區，他生前未有就學及工作。警員在案發現場檢查死者手機，發現手機內有賭波應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者在中學時期患上抑鬱症，一直有社工跟進，他的情況，在近年曾有好轉。死者中六畢業後，再無升學或就業，變成「雙失青年」，近三年來，在家中<span style=\"color: red;\">打機度日</span>，懷疑因病自尋短見，暫時並無發現遺書，相信事件無可疑。大棠郊野公園楓香林為本港的賞紅葉勝地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175028/%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E6%A5%93%E9%A6%99%E6%9E%97-%E9%9B%99%E5%A4%B1%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E5%BA%A6%E6%97%A5-%E5%BB%BF%E6%AD%B2%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E7%94%B7-%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%A0%E6%B6%BC%E4%BA%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F175028%2F%25E9%25AD%2582%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25A5%2593%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%259E%2597-%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25BB%25BF%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A3%25A0%25E6%25B6%25BC%25E4%25BA%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B8%258A%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bcb343e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175028/%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E6%A5%93%E9%A6%99%E6%9E%97-%E9%9B%99%E5%A4%B1%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E5%BA%A6%E6%97%A5-%E5%BB%BF%E6%AD%B2%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E7%94%B7-%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%A0%E6%B6%BC%E4%BA%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E4%BA%A1</a>"},{"pid":"f36f52a9071d242ade9a8bff59f5de27a3add00f","tid":618068,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-0